          "reviewBody": "I had visited the school and found Very Arrogant Receiptionist. I had visited 3-4 times for Admission for Kids of My Friend and the lady behaves like she is the owner of the School and decison maker. Asking for Admission form she ask for Money but with same thing she says no guarantee for admission as classes are full. secondly upon Requesting that can you please share honourable trustee's name,she denies to share.today after loads of argument Honourable BOD Lunavatji the Senior most person called me to hear the reason of argument but he was Kind enough to Listen  her ,when it was my Turn to say my side..he straight away said no Admission...is it the way to do Justice. Reviews for school teachers and education is good but they should teach their staff to be polite...That was my observation.",
